OL,3,CWidows 'turn pain into purpose' to
OL,4,Ctackle loneliness over Christmas
OL,6,FA group of widows are campaigning to
OL,7,F'turn pain into purpose' over the
OL,8,FChristmas period for those who have
OL,9,Flost a loved one.
OL,11,FThe 'Widowed Collective' brings
OL,12,Ftogether those dealing with grief
OL,13,Fafter the death of a partner.
OL,15,FThey say their work becomes even more
OL,16,Fimportant during the festive period,
OL,17,Fwhen those grieving can often struggle
OL,18,Fthe most.
