OL,3,CWidows 'turn pain into purpose' to
OL,4,Ctackle loneliness over Christmas
OL,6,FNatalie Bolton lost her partner
OL,7,FJonathan suddenly on Mother's Day 2021
OL,8,Fto a cardiac arrest, leaving her to
OL,9,Fraise their twin daughters alone `
OL,10,Ftheir first Christmas was so painful
OL,11,Fshe fled the country.
OL,13,FNatalie: "It's just dread really, it
OL,14,Fjust fills me with dread. The first
OL,15,Ffew years I've really ran away, I
OL,16,Fdidn't face Christmas at all.
