OL,3,CWidows 'turn pain into purpose' to
OL,4,Ctackle loneliness over Christmas
OL,6,F"This year is the first year I'm going
OL,7,Fto be cooking and hosting and my girls
OL,8,Fare older now, so we can do it
OL,9,Ftogether, but certainly when they were
OL,10,Fyounger it was awful, so painful."
OL,12,FHeather Smith, from Stockport, lost
OL,13,Fher partner four-and-a-half years ago,
OL,14,Fafter he died from kidney cancer just
OL,15,Fthree days before their daughter's
OL,16,Fseventh birthday.
OL,18,FHeather said: "That first Christmas in
OL,19,Fparticular really hit hard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
