OL,3,CWidows 'turn pain into purpose' to
OL,4,Ctackle loneliness over Christmas
OL,6,F"It was around six months after I lost
OL,7,Fmy husband and I had two young
OL,8,Fchildren aged seven and three at
OL,9,FChristmas, and you've got to try and
OL,10,Fkeep some sort of magic alive for
OL,11,Fthem, but you just feel like you just
OL,12,Fwant to hide.
OL,14,F"How I've got through it is you just
OL,15,Fhave to take each day at a time... and
OL,16,Fwhat really helped me as well was
OL,17,Freaching out to other people in my
OL,18,Fsituation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
