OL,3,CWidows 'turn pain into purpose' to
OL,4,Ctackle loneliness over Christmas
OL,6,FShe continued: "Every aspect of your
OL,7,Flife changes when you're widowed and
OL,8,Fjust being around people that get that
OL,9,Fand who you can have a shoulder to cry
OL,10,Fon with, but you can also have a laugh
OL,11,Fwith.
OL,13,F"That's really what got me through
OL,14,Fthat first Christmas, and Christmas'
OL,15,Fsince."
OL,17,FRosie Moss' husband grew up in
OL,18,FManchester, he vanished during a
OL,19,Fdiving accident, and his body has
OL,20,Fnever been recovered.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
