OL,3,CWidows 'turn pain into purpose' to
OL,4,Ctackle loneliness over Christmas
OL,6,FRosie said: "I think there's an
OL,7,Fenormous power in saying no, I think
OL,8,Fthat's a word you have to utilise a
OL,9,Flot when you're widowed. And by doing
OL,10,Fthings that work for you and your
OL,11,Ffamily.
OL,13,F"But I do think that kind of pacing
OL,14,Fyourself and only taking on what you
OL,15,Fcan manage - and the power in that
OL,16,Fword no."
OL,18,FNicky Wake lost her husband Andy in
OL,19,F2020, and decided to launch the group
OL,20,Fto help people navigate their grieving
OL,21,Fjourney.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
