OL,3,CWidows 'turn pain into purpose' to
OL,4,Ctackle loneliness over Christmas
OL,6,FHer husband died following years of
OL,7,Fcomplications from a catastrophic
OL,8,Fcardiac arrest, spending multiple
OL,9,FChristmases parenting alone while
OL,10,Fnavigating hospital care and
OL,11,Funcertainty.
OL,13,F"Lean into the widow community. We are
OL,14,Fhere," she said.
OL,16,FWe're hosting weekly Zoom's on a
OL,17,FMonday night at seven o'clock that
OL,18,Fanyone who is widowed can join, and
OL,19,Fyou don't even need to talk, you can
OL,20,Fjust sit and listen. And listen to
OL,21,Fother people's experience.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
