OL,3,CWidows 'turn pain into purpose' to
OL,4,Ctackle loneliness over Christmas
OL,6,F"We've got a Whatsapp group, so
OL,7,Fthere's always someone to talk to day
OL,8,Fand night. And we've also got online
OL,9,Fforums so you don't have to do this on
OL,10,Fyour own. There are other people who
OL,11,Freally understand, and will be here to
OL,12,Fsupport you through it."
